description: Watch the video, explore the virtual tour and check all of the photos. Welcome to the nicest and best located Penthouse Condo at Villas Del Rey, a relaxing oasis, in the heart of Silicone Beach. Enjoy the natural light pouring in from the tall, vaulted ceilings. Relax in privacy off the street and shaded by bamboo. Be proud of your custom built kitchen when your friends are over. Laugh and love more in your open living room and dining room with remodeled fireplace. Feel blessed every time you walk into your Carrara marble bathrooms. Feel the openness when your barbequing on the balcony, watching the sunset through the sky. Upgrades: quartz kitchen with waterfall breakfast bar and glass tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, farmhouse sink, in unit washer and dryer, stone fireplace mantel, luxury vinyl floors, Carrara marble bathroom floors with custom vanities, custom showers and custom bath. HOA Amenities: pool, spa, two tennis courts, onsite maintenance, men's and women's saunas, men's and women's bathrooms, wonderful landscaping.

This is a luxurious three bedroom and 2 full bathroom. The living area is 1,755 square feet Featuring open space living, dining and kitchen area with inside laundry facility and a 290 square feet two-car-garage making a total of 2,045 feet structure. This unit has been remodeled two years ago with new plumbing, Electrical, subfloor and floor, new windows. Additionally, "Santiago Estate park" offers pool, basketball, hand ball and BBQ area for residents all included in the land lease. Buyer is responsible of their own due diligence and investigation.

OFFERS DUE NOVEMBER 3, 2022 BY 5PM. Value and incredible opportunity in Willowbrook. Great income property for a seasoned investor or someone looking to get started. Easy access to freeways, school and public transportation. Two units, one 1bed/1ba, second 2bed/2ba with front garage and covered patio in the yard. Drive by only. PROPERTY IS TENANT OCCUPIED Do Not Disturb tenants. Group showings will be arranged.

Updated & Modern * 2,604sqft * 11,755sqft Lot * 4 Bedrooms / 4 Bathrooms * 2,604sqft * 11,755sqft Lot * Open Floor Plan * Large Kitchen With Center Island * Dining Area * Huge Family Room * Bright * All Appliances Included * Large Master Bedroom With Walk-In Closet * Tile & Laminate Floors * Central A/C & Heat * CCTV Throughout * Built In Speakers *  Entertainers Backyard * Pool & Spa * Rooftop Deck With Breathtaking Views * Custom Fire Pit * Laundry Location In The Garage * 2 Car Garage * You Don’t Want To Miss This One!

Polished, sophisticated details and plenty of space to start and end each day! This flawless West Hills two-story home sits on a 12,840-SqFt lot, it features a spacious floorplan with 4-bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an office and 2,165-SqFt of living space. Throughout this newly painted home find bright rooms with laminate flooring, recessed lighting, built-ins, dual pane windows, ample storage space and much more! Spend your evenings at home relaxing in the living room next to the modern stone fireplace or make your way to the formal dining area where you can enjoy the view of the yard. The easy backyard access makes entertaining a lot more convenient! Through the dining area find a guest bathroom and a well-equipped kitchen that has top of the line NEW stainless-steel appliances, a tiled subway backsplash, quartz countertops and custom cabinets. Kitchen also includes a coffee bar area. All 3 bathroom have been updated with stylish fixtures. The primary bedroom has a custom painted wall and a private ensuite bathroom that has a sliding barn door, a spa tub and separate shower. Outside presents a picturesque yard with an open patio featuring drought proof landscaping with artificial turf grass and pavers, a built-in BBQ and lots of privacy. Take pleasure entertaining your family and friends while you BBQ or add outdoor seating to the patio and unwind after a long day in solitude. This corner lot property that is in a sought-after neighborhood. It has a 2-car garage, and it is surrounded with lush greenery, perfect for that extra needed privacy. Property has a tankless water heater. 2-car garage has approved JADU plans should new buyer want to convert the structure. Less than 5 miles from the Westfield Topanga & The Village, Costco, Pierce College, the Warner Center, and Chatsworth Nature Preserve!
4 bedroom, 2 bathroom single story home in North Hollywood. Flat lot, and detached 2 car garage. Photos provided by tenants. More details and professional photos to come soon.

This is a construction project for builders/flippers/developers etc. Price reflects project condition. Private financing or cash offers only. 2 Lots and an amazing opportunity with a massive price drop to boot. Create the perfect dream home in Laurel Canyon. The home will boast over 1,800 square feet of indoor and outdoor covered living spaces. There is a great sense of seclusion whilst being minutes away from Sunset Blvd and best of Hollywood. The home features multiple patios and decks allowing full usage of views, views, views and privacy that surround this amazing property which is located in the Wonderland School District. There is also ample land to create a dream garden. The property has 2 lots, allowing its new owner to build a possible new ADU or...... Agents please do not call listing agent before you read comments and download all documents.

Stylish and set in a peaceful neighborhood, this amazing LA abode has been beautifully updated and will take your breath away! Built in 1912, it's a stunning example of the traditional Craftsman style with incredible curb appeal and plenty of natural light flowing through abundant windows. Much of the classic design has been retained, including the original front door, its expansive front porch, and the impeccable millwork inside. New wide-plank flooring and baseboards in the fireplace-warmed living room continue across the seamlessly connected gathering areas.    Coffered ceilings grace the dining room, and the adjacent kitchen has been renovated with quartz countertops, painted cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Your main bedroom has an ensuite with direct access to the deck. As a bonus, there's a second kitchen and a bathroom in the garage (Buyer to verify if permitted). An HVAC system, copper plumbing, plus recessed and modern lighting add to the home's appeal. The desirable location places you near Vermont Square Park and local eateries like South LA Cafe. Come take a tour before this gem is gone for good!

Beautiful pool home located on a quiet and private cul-de-sac at the base of the Angeles National Forest, this view home was completely updated in 2017 with the help of a designer to maximize storage space and convenience and checks all of the boxes. The kitchen is beautifully updated with quartz counter tops, high end fixtures, soft close cabinets with pull-out shelving and drawers, and stainless-steel appliances. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet designed by Closet World plus an additional closet, a picture window and a beautifully updated bathroom with two large recessed built-in medicine cabinets with electrical outlets.  All bathroom cabinets are soft close and pull-out shelving.  There are 3 other bedrooms upstairs, another updated bathroom, tons of storage in the hallway area, a linen closet and incredible mountain views.  The living room opens to the dining room and is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen has an eat in bar, an eating area with storage, bench seating and is open to the bright and airy family room which features a fireplace and opens to the outdoor patio. The corner lot features a private gated back yard and a heated Pebble Tec pool and spa. The downstairs office has a closet and can be used as a 5th bedroom and opens up to the patio. Other features include central air and heat, a central vacuum, copper plumbing and updated electric service, Milgard dual pane windows, decorative Titan security screen door, an attached 2 car garage with ample storage and a drip system for all of the outdoor plants.

A rare must see masterpiece!  Hundreds of thousands spent to create this extensive designer remodel and expansion in 2018.  Truly one of the FINEST VIEW homes in the desirable Highlander Park community. Plus, award winning charter schools! Delight in the breathtaking SUNRISES and the burnt Sienna SUNSETS with panoramic views of The Warner Center visible from your front yard, entryway, living room, dining room, master bedroom, bathroom and backyard.  Fine finishes, attention to detail and custom artistic and architectural touches are highlighted throughout.  A few of the Masterpiece touches include: New/Newer: exterior and interior paint, Challenger Superlawn Xtreme 80 oz artificial turf, sprinkler valves, timer, 1 drip emitter PER PLANT (200 individual DRIP emitters) Rheem 4 ton rooftop package, ductwork and air vents, 30 year roof, fascia boards, electrical panel, wiring, water heater, copper plumbing, dual pane windows, aluminum reinforced poly shutters, exterior doors, interior frosted doors, door hardware, 6 inch baseboards, Decora outlets and switches, Energy Star LED recessed lights, Nest thermostat, water heater, expanded kitchen, center island, Kenmore 45 bottle wine chiller, pendant lights, Shaker style cabinets, over counter lights, Moen basin, Water Creation faucet, sugar white quartz countertops, Tuileries tile, Kenmore Elite appliance which include a dishwasher, gas range and microwave/convection oven, WALKER ZANGER custom tile throughout. Master Bathroom EXPANDED, walk-in closet with custom built-ins and Milgard quad 189.5 x 79.5.  Outdoor pool shower, Hayward pool pump, filter, heater and light, IntelliBrite ambient pool light controller, pool plaster and tile, custom cement bench and complementary matching fire pit. Newer office/playroom/fitness room with barn door to laundry area and approximately 5 x 20 storage room.  MUCH MUCH MORE!  Enjoy nearby world class shopping, fine dining and tranquil hikes through Victory Trailhead Park.

Walnut Acres completely remodeled and expanded single story pool home with ADU potential located on a 14k lot! Situated behind private security gates with superb 150+ feet of sprawling frontage, this ranch home has been completely renovated with bespoke designer finishes. The privately gated front yard boasts brand new landscaping and new paver stone driveway for 4+ cars/RV/boat that leads to a detached finished garage perfect for office/ADU with separate laundry room and half bath. A covered front porch greets you before entering the home’s completely open floor plan. The large sunlit family room boasts vaulted wood beamed ceiling, wood mantled fireplace, large picture windows, and new vinyl floors found throughout. The stunningly chic, completely remodeled chef’s kitchen opens directly to the family room and boasts large center island with quartz counter and breakfast bar seating, gun metal appliances including an Ilve range, soft close black slate cabinetry, custom wine storage built-in, and tiled backsplash. There is a separate dining area off the kitchen with two sets of sliders that lead out to the backyard. The massive expanded primary suite features vaulted wood beamed ceiling, new large walk-in closet, and private completely new bathroom with dual sinks, large walk-in shower with dual raindrop shower heads, designer tile, and private door out to the yard. There are two additional secondary bedrooms, one of which has a door out to the yard ideal for office. Both secondary rooms share an upgraded hall bathroom with tub/shower combo. The backyard is an entertainer’s delight boasting newly pebble finished swimming pool and spa with rock waterfall feature, new custom built covered patio lounging deck, separate wraparound covered patio, and multiple grassy lawns. Additional upgrades per seller: new roof, new HVAC, new tankless water heater, new Milgard windows and doors, new pool/spa heater, new fencing/gate, and new “cooling” exterior paint. Zoned for award-winning El Camino and Hale charter schools, and close to dining/shopping at The Commons & Westfield Mall & Village.

Price Improvement! Mid-Century STUNNER in a quiet neighborhood in Winnetka! Priced to sell and it's first time on the market in 35+ years! Kitchen has been updated with quartz countertop and classic white cabinets with original midcentury floor tiles. New range and newer microwave and refrigerator included in sale. Expanded main living space is perfect for daily living and entertaining. 3 bedrooms have lots of natural light and great sized closets. Both bathrooms were tastefully updated 3 years ago. Detached garage has room for 2 cars or potential ADU for extra income. Backyard has fresh new concrete pad for low maintenance and great useability. HVAC was replaced in 2017! Plumbing is copper! Windows and sliding door are dual paned!

Impressive and sophisticated Penthouse unit in the highly desired Encino Spa East.  Nearly 2000 square feet of living area that seems larger and with soaring 15+ foot ceilings.  Gorgeous hardwood floors.  Chef's galley kitchen with granite counters,  electric cooktop, double ovens, refrigerator, dishwasher, dual sinks, microwave, glass faced cabinetry, Pfister designer plumbing fixtures, recessed lighting, and so many cabinets. Great spacious living room with the dining area just off the kitchen and living rooms.  Impressive gas fireplace in the living accented with custom shelving.  Amazing wall space for your art work. Fabulous wood shutters throughout the unit gives a great accent to all rooms. Great balcony off of the living room opens this floorplan for great entertaining.  There is a wet bar with a separate built in wine refrigerator.  The primary suite is right out of Park Avenue complete with quartz counters, dual sinks, separate vanity, mirrored walls, custom shelving, and beautiful walk-in shower, and Delta plumbing fixtures.  The spacious walk in closet is complete with custom shelving systems. Closet space galore in this one as well. Up top is the loft great for a home office, study, or den with it's own powder room that opens to the most amazing "private" roof top deck that is just spectacular for dining, entertaining, relaxing, and oh those views out to the mountains, hills, and vistas...WOW!  Truly amazing! Laundry is just off the kitchen with its' own service door. Flooring is a nice combo of hardwoods, tile, stone, and berber carpeting.  Parking in the gated garage is side by side and the unit does have it's own storage.  The HOA includes EQ insurance, water, pool, spa, sauna, clubhouse, and basic cable.  Gorgeous lush greenbelt through the grounds.  Very rarely does a unit come up for sale in this highly sought after community...let alone a west facing Penthouse...here it is. Close to the Boulevard, shopping, dining, easy freeway access, and medical offices.

Calling Entertainer's for this move in ready tastefully remodeled home just bring a toothbrush! This original design by famed Architect Charles Du Bois who was known for the modern mid-century design in the 1950's and 1960's. Enter the stylish mid-century front door into a vast open concept living/dining room. The covered patio off the Great Room offers additional space for indoor/outdoor entertaining... perfect California living.  Cozy up with drinks or a book in front of the gas fireplace with glass rocks lit and its attractive stone facade. View the large kitchen with granite counters, stainless appliances, lots of storage, and the pantry/laundry room just beyond. This well-maintained home has two spacious master's and three baths, one bath with spa tub. The largest master has ADU potential (with minor construction) or could be used as a creative workspace for music, audio/visual, vlogging, dance studio or more just use your imagination. Enjoy the fruit trees and newly installed drought tolerant landscape. Starbucks, restaurant's, markets, a park, a public pool, and more are just minutes away. Buyer's to do their due diligence for all matters including ADU possibility.

Remodeled West Hills 3+2 Single Story Open Living Concept Home in the El Camino Charter School District with Paid Solar, Indoor Laundry and a Nice Size Yard! Did we mention it is in the El Camino Charter School District?? The interior highlights of this home includes new HVAC, new furnace, new ducting, new flooring, new baseboards, new recessed lighting, ceiling fans and more. Upon entering this beauty find the light and bright great room, dining area that has views of the yard. Stunning cooks’ kitchen with new quartz counters, and backsplash, updated cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and bay window. Good-sized bedrooms with mirrored wardrobe doors, and two bathrooms, one with a custom wood accent wall. Outside find an artificially turfed front yard with lush landscaping, two car attached garage, extra wide driveway, lovely backyard with lots of fruit trees, including lime and apple. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this your NEXT HOME!!!

Back on the market at no fault of seller!!!, Residing on a private cul-de-sac in historic Sylmar is this perfect, completely remodeled condo! Boasting a bright 1,146-sqft floor plan of 3-beds, 2-baths, inside is gorgeous tile flooring outlined with baseboard molding installed all throughout, high ceilings equipped with recessed lights, and lovely lighting fixtures for an extra dash of style. The sizable living room is the perfect entertainment space with a relaxing fireplace to curl up next to during those colder months or enjoy the outdoor scenery from the private balcony. A monochromatic palette is showcased in this galley style kitchen offering flawless granite countertops with a gorgeous decorative tile backsplash, plenty of sleek cabinetry with modern hardware, built-in stainless-steel appliances, plus a darling breakfast nook at the end of the space. All bedrooms are beyond spacious with tons of natural light illuminating the rooms and offering ample closet space. The large primary bedroom includes the exclusive benefit of an en-suite split bath with dual sink vanities and a walk-in closet. As an added plus, the home has a 2-car garage with a convenient laundry area. Featured within a charming, gated community offering to all residents a beautifully clean exterior with a community pool, spa, seating areas, and tons of visitor parking Located near USPS, Vons, Vallarta Supermarkets, Arco, Starbucks, various restaurants, local shops, as well as easy access to the 210-Freeways, and more!

Welcome home! Nestled in a quiet neighborhood just off the 118 freeway, this gorgeous, TURNKEY townhome is situated in the Sayre Village gated community. Newly remodeled, this spacious home features 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, high ceilings, and a bonus room which can be used as a 3rd bedroom or office. Brand new kitchen with new cabinets, stove, microwave, dishwasher, walk-in pantry, and stunning quartz countertops. Enter inside to a multi-level, open floor plan with 1,366 sq ft of modern living space, where an elegant living room and dining room feature sleek, vinyl plank wood flooring, large windows, a private patio for sunny days and a brick fireplace for cozy nights. The Master bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, ceiling fan, and private balcony. The 2nd bedroom enjoys a full, ensuite bathroom, large closet, and ceiling fan. The laundry room is in the unit and offers ample storage space. New central A/C, heat, water heater, and garage door opener. All with the added benefits of a private, two car garage with direct access to the home, plus two community pools and guest parking in a peaceful complex. The HOA dues include the bills for water, trash, pool, landscaping, and insurance! This commuter-friendly home is centrally located in close proximity to the 210, 5, 118, and 405 freeways, schools, library, shopping, restaurants, parks, hiking trails, golf courses, Hansen Dam soccer complex, Hansen Dam aquatic center, and the Discovery Cube Los Angeles. This home can be shown 7 days a week, so call for your appointment today. It’s a must-see and won’t last long!

Call Brandon King Home Selling Team for a private showing 800-551-1727
Glassell Park View Home + Pool and ADU! Needs TLC and is a fixer. Vintage home with hand-painted tiled kitchen, pantry and bath. Dining room off the kitchen has large glass sliding doors to the pool and patio. Hardwood floors. This home has 2 bedrooms on the main level and a third bedroom in the attic area with amazing views. Main level has a den/office space off the living room with wall to wall views. Wood burning stove in the living room provides heat during the holidays or cold winter nights. Lower level has been modified into an ADU with a separate entrance, bath and laundry room, making it ideal for guests or rental opportunities. Two-car garage.

A spectacular 5-bed, 4-bath single-story home poised for the taking in Northridge! Entering this gated picture-perfect home,  you are greeted with a brick accented fireplace, wood floors, recessed lighting, and large windows providing ample amount of natural light. With 2,480 sqft of living space and over 10,000 sqft lot, the home has a formal dining area, a kitchen with wood cabinets, and five large bedrooms and solar panels installed! Home has new wood floors, interior paint, upgraded bathrooms, double pane windows.  Perfect for ADU conversion! Solar is a lease at $170 a month with 12 years remaining, buyer to assume the lease. Attached 1 bedroom guest quarters with separate entrance. The entertainers backyard has a partially covered patio area and lawn area, perfect for entertaining guests or hosting large gatherings!

Welcome to this turn-key home conveniently located in a desiring area of Los Angeles! This is a great opportunity for a starting family ready to move in! This home features a spacious area throughout: 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, home has a bonus room with bathroom that can be used as a family room or bedroom use. Moving over this home has all the desiring features: LVT flooring throughout the house and tile, the kitchen was totally upgraded quartz counter tops and wood cabinets in the kitchen. New paint throughout the interior and exterior, new front door installed, new ceilings installed, new closet doors in the bedrooms, some new windows, all bathrooms were all upgraded with shower walls, shower, toilets, sink and vanity. Some electrical and plumbing was upgrades. Long drive way with enough space for multiple cars to park. Conveniently located near all amenities including entertaining & shopping centers, educational schools, city transportation, walking distance from the Banc of California Stadium (home of the new LAFC champions), University of Southern California, Los Angeles Memorial Coliseum and 110 freeway. Don't miss out!
This is a single family home, that has 3 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. It is located in Los Angeles, California.

Live in the highly sought after Osage neighborhood of Westchester!  With well thought-out updates, this turn key home is comfortable, stylish, and functional. Just minutes from great dining, grocery and department stores along Sepulveda Blvd. A short drive to the beach, minutes to the heart of Silicon Beach and Playa Vista, the Westfield Shopping Center, SoFi Stadium; and for those jet setters, a short drive to LAX. The location doesn't get better than this. Fresh paint and contemporary finishes with new landscaping offer eye-catching curb appeal. As you open the front door, you are welcomed by a light and bright living room with newly refinished hardwood floors. The dining area extends into an inviting backyard deck perfect to enjoy the warm Summer evenings or for entertaining family and friends.  In the large grassy backyard, mature trees provide privacy, shade, avocados and lemons.  Enjoy preparing home cooked meals in the well appointed kitchen with Viking appliances and granite countertops. Three bedrooms with updated built-in closets, two bathrooms, and a finished two car garage with EV charger makes a perfect bonus space with endless potential. Don't miss this opportunity to own in one of Westchester's great neighborhoods.

Indulge in the privacy, style, and space offered in this tastefully remodeled home within the Granada Hills charter school system. Situated on a cul de sac this property has a lot to offer. As you arrive to the tucked away home you are greeted with a double door iron gate which opens up to a grand newly remodeled driveway that is lined with mature palm trees which leads you down to the house. This bright and airy home features 3 bed 3 bath and sits on a 14,098 sqft lot with 2,371 sqft of living space. Immediately upon entering the property you are welcomed by a large foyer giving you a warm at home feeling with a perfect floor plan for entertaining family and friends during any special occasion. Walk into a freshly painted living area with vaulted ceilings and a grand stone fireplace. Enjoy some beautiful views of the hills and valleys from the living area, dining, family room, kitchen and master. The family room and master open up to large deck with a wide fire pit which offers a sitting area to relax after a long day. This home was completely remodeled almost 2 years ago. Some of the upgrades are new roof, 2 brand new central ac systems, bathrooms, kitchen, flooring, driveway, shutter windows. The remodeled kitchen has a large pantry, laundry area and a bay window so you can enjoy some of the views from there as well. New stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting throughout and so much more! This home also comes with a completely paid off solar paneling system. Centrally located to lots of restaurants, stores and 405 freeway.

Rare opportunity to buy the best view in town from the owner. 2% to buyer's agent. Half commissions - the savings goes to you. We are in escrow to buy another place and must sell now! Cash offers with a fast close will be discounted and considered first. Proof of funds required. You will not believe the views. They are the very best in town. And it comes with a pretty great house as well. 4 BR, 5BA, Mid- Mod. Fully remodeled in 2008. Text first. 818 335 3533 . Eddie

Value range listing $1,199,999 - $1,350,000. Candy cane lane neighborhood at the south end of collage acres. Beautifully remodeled home on a huge lot with resort like yard with salt water pool.  Total open floor plan. 1 master bedroom with access to the yard downstairs with one more bedroom. Upstairs the new master bedroom with one more bedroom.  NO agents please. I’m an agent helping family.  Call me directly at 818-350-3005

Amazing opportunity for owner-user or investor! This ready-to-fix property in an up and coming neighborhood in Silverlake Echo Park area is being offered for the first time since 1975. Assessor shows 2 units total of 4 bedrooms 3 baths, 2-car detached garage at the end of a long driveway, perfect for multiple vehicles. Looking for a project in a gentrifying area? This one is a true fixer with unlimited potential and it's easy to show. Property will be delivered vacant. Attractions such as Walt Disney Concert Hall, Hollywood Bowl and Dodger Stadium are all within minutes. Must see!

Fabulous Views ! South of The Blvd Prime Studio City Location! Situated within the highly desirable Carpenter Ave Elementary School District. Custom newly built in 2005, Move-in ready and impeccably maintained. This immaculate opportunity of a property features soaring 18 ft high ceilings, Custom Hunter Douglas Window Treatments, grand foyer entry, formal living room, and a hand carved fireplace mantel. An entertainers, larger formal dining room leading to the private lower patio, all ideal for large family gatherings. Gourmet kitchen features an expansive center island prep area, a chef's dream for cooking and Holiday gatherings of family & friends. Functional for everyday use, and family living. The kitchen features double bullnose granite countertops, travertine backsplash, All stainless, Jade appliances, Dual door Sub-Zero fridge/freezer, built-in microwave, and a refrigerated wine cooler.  The family room features a custom fireplace, wall mounted TV, built in surround sound system, a huge bay window overlooks the entire valley below. Easy access from the main area level to the laundry room,all ensuite bedroom, & guest powder room. All upstairs bedrooms are ensuite featuring walk in closets, dual pane Milgard windows, custom spanish doors, high ceilings, custom crown mouldings & baseboards. Full expansive view deck w/access from the master suite & 2nd bedroom. The master suite features a private entry to the walled back patio, seasoned bougainvillea trees & formal sitting areas. A romantic fireplace is featured in the Master Suite, direct upper deck access for an "all evening" valley views. The private master bath features an oversized jacuzzi tub, large glass enclosed travertine shower, dressing areas w/proper lighting for vanity make-up areas, huge walk in closet, shoe racks,and loads of linen storage. This is a wonderful entertainers home featuring privacy, easy maintenance, room for expansion, totally private yard, upper deck outdoor space, large three car, easy access garage, newer HVAC systems, updated alarm and lighting. Excellent location, easy access and walking distance to all local restaurants, enterianiment, and local businesses. Grab this opportunity for a solid, well built home constructed all new in 2005! Some photos are virtually furnished, Enjoy !

Price reduced for immediate sale!  Fabulous owner/user triplex located in prime Hollywood Hills. Two bedroom unit features many original period details.  Step down living room with fireplace, hardwood floors, high ceilings, gourmet granite kitchen, recessed lighting and updated baths. Master with en-suite, 2nd bedroom with built in bookshelves, Front deck off the living room offers lovely canyon views. Large private rear patio with fireplace. Two additional updated units provide great income. A wonderful opportunity to own a unique and special property, in one of LA's best locations!

Welcome to the fantastic city of Lake Balboa! This newly remodeled property features a 4 bedroom 2 bathroom main house + a 400 square foot 1 bedroom 1 bathroom FULLY PERMITTED JADU. IN ADDITION, the lot features the opportunity to build a 1,200-square-foot ADU in the backyard! Recent upgrades include a NEW roof, NEW flooring, remodeled bathrooms, solar panels, and interior/exterior paint. As a current Airbnb, this property has an average of $10,000/month in revenue, with a high of $14,000! All Airbnb and rental permits will be transferred to the new owner with the sale of the property if desired, and the current management company will gladly come to terms with the new owner if desired. Enjoy close proximity to Lake Balboa Park, Van Nuys/Woodley Lakes Golf Course, Encino Farmer's Market, Sepulveda Basin Off-Leash Park, Los Angeles Metro Orange Line-Balboa Station, bike trails, and easy freeway access. Book an appointment to view this extraordinary property today!

Lovely 1967 Spanish-style home sited on a prime parcel moments south of Brentwood Country Mart. Four-bedroom, 3-bath, light-filled home w/excellent floor plan on quiet flag lot shielded from street. First floor: formal entry & staircase, powder room, generous living room w/FP & access to bucolic rear garden. Large updated kitchen / family room w/dining area. Direct access to 2-car garage & laundry. Second floor: spacious primary suite w/dressing room & updated bath. Three additional bedrooms plus large updated bath completes floor. Outside living areas include side garden ideal for dining, rear garden w/enchanting views of contiguous estate properties, and front motor court (accommodates multiple vehicles) is lushly planted. Property is located in Los Angeles w/City of LA services yet maintains a Santa Monica mailing address.

Presenting a pristine single level condo in Toluca Lake with a fantastic location! This condo is in a gorgeous complex built in 2006 which is on the ground floor and has over 1300 square feet. There are high ceilings, recessed lighting, hardwood floors, and an oversized private outdoor patio off the living room. The master suite is large with walk-in closet, plus a spa style master bath with soaking tub, separate shower, and stone tile and counters. The gourmet kitchen is generously sized with granite counters and stainless steel appliances, there is a huge formal dining room with buffet bar and loads of cabinets for storage. The HVAC system was recently replaced, there are 2 subterranean parking spaces, and the garage features lots of additional guest parking. This location is a 10+ with easy access to fabulous dining, boutiques, NBC, and Universal Studios. This building has elevators for easy accessibility, there is a lovely courtyard with fountain, and a rooftop deck setup for parties and BBQ. Come make this your dream home today!

Presenting this beautiful hilltop home with magnificent views in Monterey Hills adjacent to Highland Park. You have a view of the city and tree tops from almost every room in this house This home has 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms on the main floor and family room with full bathroom downstairs. The master bedroom features a walk-closet and a private bathroom with dual sinks, separate shower and tub. This property features an open floor plan living/dining room, wrap around porch, central AC, laundry hookup, avocado tree, recessed lighting, wired security system and so much more. This home was updated 70% a few years back and in the most recent years a new sewer line, new custom doors and a drainage system. Conveniently located a few blocks from the Metro station that can take you to DTLA and Old Town Pasadena in minutes. The front yard and detached 2 car garage can be converted to an ADU and as an added bonus you can convert downstairs family room with bathroom to a jr. ADU. Watch the sunset every evening with cashflow. Don't miss out on this great opportunity.

Welcome to 2270 Cavanagh Circle, an architectural Mid Century Modern gem in the University Hills neighborhood of El Sereno. From the moment you walk up to this one-of-a-kind home, you will be blown away by the stunning views. The huge rooftop deck offers 360 views of all LA has to offer, from downtown to the mountains and everything in between - truly an amazing sight to behold.But that's not all! Boasting 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, new stone counters and brand new white oak hardwood floors. You'll love the sleek and stylish design of this home, perfect for anyone who loves modern decor. Plus, there is a wrap around deck with plenty of space for outdoor dining and relaxation in the hot tub. This unique home also features a studio with its own private entrance and bathroom. Perfect for guests or it could also be used as an office or art studio. If you're looking for a one-of-a-kind home with amazing views in a peaceful and serene setting, come see 2270 Cavanagh Circle today!
